DataGridBWP
======================

Questions & Comments
---------------------

Please visit: http://groups.google.com/group/blazelibs

Source Code
---------------

The code is available from the `bitbucket repo <http://bitbucket.org/rsyring/datagridbwp/>`_.

The `DataGridBWP tip <http://bitbucket.org/rsyring/datagridbwp/get/tip.zip#egg=DataGridBWP-dev>`_
is installable via `easy_install` with ``easy_install DataGridBWP==dev``
